org.efaps.update

Class AbstractUpdate.Link

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.efaps.update.AbstractUpdate.Link
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractUpdate.OrderedLink, AbstractUpdate.UniqueLink
    Enclosing class:
    AbstractUpdate

    protected static class AbstractUpdate.Link
extends Object
    The class is used to define the links with all information needed to update the link information between the object to update and the related objects.
    See Also:
    #setLinksInDB
